paragraphs.text: nigiri shimeta kimi no te kara kanjita furue ga setsunaku fureru tabi ni kimi no kokyuu tsutawatteta
kumi dasu koto wo akirameta kimi sotto dakiyoseta
kazoe kirenu namida no wake kitto kanashimi no kizuato semete mirai ni nagareru namida wo kaerarete

genshoku de karamiau bashou he kimi wo michibiku zutto kono te wa
kimi he sashi obeteru delicated to being now link a flashy emotion being held by dazzling take my prime step forward
for all time tashika na mono ga koko ni aru kara shinjiteite
kotae wa itsumo mugen no bazuru tesaguri no mira me ga kuramu hodo hikaru asu wo sono me ni miseyou genshoku de tsunagareta
kimi wo mamori tsudzukeyou kimi ga kaereru
bashou wa itsumo soba ni kimi no ikiru imi wo tsukuri ageru kara
